, 
<figureCitation box="[257,288,186,210]" captionStart="FIGURES 49–58" captionStartId="61.[151,264,1277,1300]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,193,1256]" captionTargetId="figure-153@61.[151,1435,193,1256]" captionTargetPageId="61" captionText="FIGURES 49–58. ♀. 49, 50, propodeum, dorsal, Holotypes. 49, Debilos masipum sp. nov. 50, D. sanimum sp. nov. 51–53, metapleuron apical fovea (arrow), metapleuron, frontal. 51, D. soror (Trentepohl), Holotype. 52, D. dnopheror sp. nov., Holotype. 53, D. frater sp. nov., Holotype. 54–58, propodeal spiracle, frontal. 54, D. palaior sp. nov., Holotype. 55, D. dialeucor sp. nov., Holotype. 56, D. typurum sp. nov., Holotype. 57, D. indistinctum sp. nov., Holotype. 58, D. trochanteratum (Szépligeti). Specimen from Brazil, RO, Candeias do Jamari, 28.I–4.II.2006 (UFES). Illustrations not to scale. Fig. 63 photographed by Berthil B. Longo." pageId="39" pageNumber="40">50</figureCitation>
