, 
<figureCitation box="[396,439,186,210]" captionStart="FIGURES 148–154" captionStartId="75.[151,263,1933,1956]" captionTargetBox="[233,1354,167,1912]" captionTargetId="figure-81@75.[233,1354,167,1912]" captionTargetPageId="75" captionText="FIGURES 148–154. Diagrams with distribution records for: 148, Debilos owinum sp. nov.; 149, D. pekujum sp. nov.; 150, D. sanimum sp. nov.; 151, D. tasamunum sp. nov.; 152, D. typurum sp. nov.; 153, D. umentum sp. nov.; 154, Debilos Townes, all records." pageId="39" pageNumber="40">150</figureCitation>
